Package gramatika

Interface gramatikaListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    gramatikaBaseListener
    public interface gramatikaListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by gramatikaParser.
